  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Eight arms at low spread, chromatophore system in resting state — the octopus at neutral, skin pattern subtle, arms minimal. Mod wheel triggers chromatophore cascade: chromaDepth and chromaSpeed accelerate in sequence, skin patterns proliferating from barely perceptible to full alien riot. At high wheel, chromaMorph shifts the filter bank and the octopus is communicating in patterns invisible to human perception. Aftertouch deploys the ink cloud: inkDensity and inkMix rise with pressure, the reverb tail darkening with displaced fluid until the signal is soaked in deep-sea turbulence. A hard release and the ink disperses. Velocity controls the initial armCount offset — the number of voices increases with strike force, from solo to full 8-arm radiance. These three gestures create a performance space with no ceiling.",
